    <stitle>TSI 96-12-15 - Installing an Electronic Hand Throttle on HEUI Engines</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi961215" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>96-12-15</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>December, 1996</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>ENGINE</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Installing an Electronic Hand Throttle on HEUI Engines</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>1000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>2000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>3000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8100</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8200</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8300</truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This TSI applies to 1000, 2000, 3000, 4000, and 8000 models with International T 444E, DT 466E,
                    and 530E HEUI engines.
                </para>
                <para>As recently announced, the Electronic Hand Throttle (toggle switch) is being incorporated as a
                    standard feature on many models with HEUI engines. This feature can be retrofitted to vehicles not
                    so equipped. The Hand Throttle switch will allow operators to increase engine idling rpm during cold
                    weather (recommended). Refer to TSI-96-12-29 for additional cold weather operation guidelines.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
