        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="21">
            <title>VEHICLES WITH CRUISE CONTROL</title>
            <para>Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612154">Figure 4</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612159">Figure 9</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215f">Figure 15</hotlnk>, or
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215k">Figure 20</hotlnk>
            </para>
            <para>Installation on these vehicles is accomplished by replacing the existing cruise ON-OFF switch
                [connected to white connector (391)] with hand throttle ON-OFF switch 2004674C1. The Vehicle Personality
                Module (VPM) must then be reprogrammed per TSI 94-08-05 to turn on the hand throttle feature. Contact
                Tech Central at 1-800-336-4500 for reprogramming assistance. Please install cold weather warm-up
                procedure label 3511961C2.
            </para>
            <para>
                <title>VEHICLES WITHOUT CRUISE CONTROL</title>
            </para>
            <para>
                <emph type="bold">1652SC, 3600</emph>
                (Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612151">Figure 1</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612152">Figure 2</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612153">Figure 3</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612154">Figure 4</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612155">Figure 5</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612156">Figure 6</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612157">Figure 7</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612158">Figure 8</hotlnk>, and
                <hotlnk xrefid="f9612159">Figure 9</hotlnk>)
            </para>
            <para>Installation on these vehicles requires mounting hand throttle ON-OFF switch 2004675C1 and hand
                throttle SET-RESUME switch 2004676C1 in existing holes or in auxiliary switch mounting panel 2500483C1.
                Install panel light 2040568C91 in this bracket, and wire to panel light circuitry. Refer to appropriate
                circuit diagram book for circuit numbers. On vehicles with automatic transmissions, install clutch
                switch jumper harness 2003444C91 at connector (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air brakes, install clutch switch bracket 1689908C1. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air or hydraulic brakes, install clutch switch 1622366C91 and connect to connector
                (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. Install jumper harness 2014921C92 by connecting it to connector (394)
                [circuits 97CF and 97AC], by connecting its white connector (391) to throttle ON-OFF switch (has white
                back), and connecting its black connector (392) to throttle SET-RESUME switch. Tie-strap the harness
                away from moving parts, and reprogram the Vehicle Personality Module (VPM) per TSI 94-08-05 to turn on
                the hand throttle feature. Contact Tech Central at 1-800-336-4500 for reprogramming assistance. Please
                install cold weather warm-up procedure label 3511961C2.
            </para>
            <para>
                <emph type="bold">3800, 4700, 4900 FBC</emph>
                (Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215a">Figure 10</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215b">Figure 11</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215c">Figure 12</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215d">Figure 13</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215e">Figure 14</hotlnk>, and
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215f">Figure 15</hotlnk>)
            </para>
            <para>Installation on these vehicles requires mounting hand throttle ON-OFF switch 2004675C1 and hand
                throttle SET-RESUME switch 2004676C1 in existing holes or in auxiliary switch mounting panel 2500483C1.
                Install panel light 2040568C91 in this bracket, and wire to panel light circuitry. Refer to appropriate
                circuit diagram book for circuit numbers. On vehicles with automatic transmissions, install clutch
                switch jumper harness 2003444C91 at connector (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air brakes, install clutch switch bracket 2018762C2. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air or hydraulic brakes, install clutch switch 1622366C91 and connect to connector
                (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. Install jumper harness 2017532C92 by connecting it to connector (394)
                [circuits 97CF and 97AC], by connecting its white connector (391) to throttle ON-OFF switch (has white
                back), and connecting its black connector (392) to throttle SET-RESUME switch. Tie-strap the harness
                away from moving parts, and reprogram the Vehicle Personality Module (VPM) per TSI 94-08-05 to turn on
                the hand throttle feature. Contact Tech Central at 1-800-336-4500 for reprogramming assistance. Please
                install cold weather warm-up procedure label 3511961C2.
            </para>
            <para>
                <emph type="bold">2000, 4000 (Except 4700, 4900 FBC), 8000</emph>
                (Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215g">Figure 16</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215h">Figure 17</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215i">Figure 18</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215j">Figure 19</hotlnk>,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215k">Figure 20</hotlnk>, and
                <hotlnk xrefid="f961215l">Figure 21</hotlnk>)
            </para>
            <para>Installation on these vehicles requires mounting hand throttle ON-OFF switch 2004675C1 and hand
                throttle SET-RESUME switch 2004676C1 in existing holes or in auxiliary switch mounting panel 2500483C1.
                Install panel light 2040568C91 in this bracket, and wire to panel light circuitry. Refer to appropriate
                circuit diagram book for circuit numbers. On vehicles with automatic transmissions, install clutch
                switch jumper harness 2003444C91 at connector (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air brakes, install clutch switch bracket 1689908C1. On vehicles with manual
                transmissions and air or hydraulic brakes, install clutch switch 1622366C91 and connect to connector
                (386) [circuits 97A and 97L]. Install jumper harness 2003446C92 by connecting it to connector (394)
                [circuits 97CF and 97AC], by connecting its white connector (391) to throttle ON-OFF switch (has white
                back), and connecting its black connector (392) to throttle SET-RESUME switch. Tie-strap the harness
                away from moving parts, and reprogram the Vehicle Personality Module (VPM) per TSI 94-08-05 to turn on
                the hand throttle feature. Contact Tech Central at 1-800-336-4500 for reprogramming assistance. Please
                install cold weather warm-up procedure label 3511961C2.
            </para>
